enhanced_by.reason: Both methods generate a random date within a specified age range, with similar input parameters.
The 'between' method can be used to set up date ranges similar to the age range used in 'birthday'.
The 'toString' method can be used to convert the generated Timestamp from 'birthday' into a string format for assertion.
The 'past' method generates a date in the past, similar to how 'birthday' generates a date within a past age range.
